    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.1",
          "pli": "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ sūcilomaṃ purisaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a man whose body hairs were needles flying through the air. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.2",
          "pli": "Tassa tā sūciyo sīse pavisitvā mukhato nikkhamanti; ",
          "en": "The needles bored into his head and out his mouth, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.3",
          "pli": "mukhe pavisitvā urato nikkhamanti; ",
          "en": "into his mouth and out his chest, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.4",
          "pli": "ure pavisitvā udarato nikkhamanti; ",
          "en": "into his chest and out his belly, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.5",
          "pli": "udare pavisitvā ūrūhi nikkhamanti; ",
          "en": "into his belly and out his thighs, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.6",
          "pli": "ūrūsu pavisitvā jaṅghāhi nikkhamanti; ",
          "en": "into his thighs and out his calves, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.7",
          "pli": "jaṅghāsu pavisitvā pādehi nikkhamanti; ",
          "en": "and into his calves and out his feet. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.8",
          "pli": "so sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … ",
          "en": "And he screamed in pain. …” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.9",
          "pli": "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe sūcako ahosi … pe …. ",
          "en": "“That being used to be an informant right here in Rājagaha. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.9:1.10",
          "pli": "Navamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
